WEBVTT

00:00:07.725 --> 00:00:11.711
笙ｪI found a faint light
in the fading dusk笙ｪ

00:00:11.712 --> 00:00:15.311
笙ｪAnd met your steady gaze笙ｪ

00:00:15.312 --> 00:00:24.132
笙ｪOne knowing glance,
and side by side we walk on笙ｪ

00:00:24.575 --> 00:00:27.061
笙ｪLonging finds no place to rest笙ｪ

00:00:27.062 --> 00:00:29.211
笙ｪThrough drifting wind and rain笙ｪ

00:00:29.212 --> 00:00:32.699
笙ｪYou are the prayer within my hands笙ｪ

00:00:32.700 --> 00:00:40.324
笙ｪA single second frozen,
tears in focus, my heart already knows笙ｪ

00:00:40.325 --> 00:00:42.786
笙ｪWe made a promise long ago笙ｪ

00:00:42.787 --> 00:00:44.786
笙ｪFor all our days to come笙ｪ

00:00:44.787 --> 00:00:48.449
笙ｪYou are the fate I cannot outrun笙ｪ

00:00:48.450 --> 00:00:53.836
笙ｪHow much must I let go
to trade for one moment?笙ｪ

00:00:53.837 --> 00:00:56.457
笙ｪHolding you close笙ｪ

00:00:56.637 --> 00:00:58.774
笙ｪWould that be enough?笙ｪ

00:00:58.775 --> 00:00:59.559
=Echoes of Love=

00:00:59.560 --> 00:01:01.499
(Adapted from the signed screenplay
Echoes of Love on Migu Reading)

00:01:01.500 --> 00:01:03.720
=Episode 14=

00:01:09.540 --> 00:01:10.579
Official Gu,

00:01:10.580 --> 00:01:12.978
this is newly brewed
Snow-Clear Plum Blossom Wine.

00:01:12.979 --> 00:01:14.299
On such a fine evening,

00:01:14.300 --> 00:01:16.099
how could we not have
good wine to accompany it?

00:01:31.940 --> 00:01:33.260
Song Zhiyun,

00:01:35.180 --> 00:01:36.659
I have something for you.

00:01:37.900 --> 00:01:39.220
What is it?

00:01:50.180 --> 00:01:52.220
This is the gold hairpin
my mother left me.

00:01:52.339 --> 00:01:53.420
She said

00:01:53.859 --> 00:01:55.659
I should give it to the one I hold dear.

00:01:57.499 --> 00:01:59.258
The Gu residence is not lavish,

00:01:59.259 --> 00:02:00.700
but we live comfortably.

00:02:01.020 --> 00:02:03.659
From now on, the account books
and storehouse keys will be kept by you.

00:02:03.660 --> 00:02:04.858
In the storeroom,

00:02:04.859 --> 00:02:06.780
if there is anything you like,

00:02:06.979 --> 00:02:08.460
you may take it at any time.

00:02:08.700 --> 00:02:10.338
If you wish to go out and travel,

00:02:10.339 --> 00:02:11.699
everyone in the Gu residence

00:02:11.980 --> 00:02:13.379
will answer to you.

00:02:15.539 --> 00:02:17.180
What do you mean by this?

00:02:30.379 --> 00:02:31.740
You once said

00:02:32.662 --> 00:02:34.022
you cared for me.

00:02:34.939 --> 00:02:36.099
Now,

00:02:36.737 --> 00:02:37.937
I wish...

00:02:45.180 --> 00:02:47.220
I wish to take your hand

00:02:47.225 --> 00:02:48.585
and grow old together.

00:02:52.140 --> 00:02:53.300
Song Zhiyun,

00:02:54.539 --> 00:02:55.900
will you?

00:03:00.339 --> 00:03:02.539
Do you even know what you are saying?

00:03:06.499 --> 00:03:07.899
Do you think speaking such vows

00:03:07.900 --> 00:03:09.500
means you truly love me?

00:03:10.460 --> 00:03:12.460
The divide of status is like a chasm.

00:03:13.212 --> 00:03:14.938
You are a noble young lord.

00:03:14.939 --> 00:03:18.020
Are you truly willing to follow the proper rites
and formally bring me into your home?

00:03:18.025 --> 00:03:19.065
I am.

00:03:24.637 --> 00:03:27.139
Have you ever considered
that being with someone like me,

00:03:27.140 --> 00:03:29.099
someone judged by the world,

00:03:30.437 --> 00:03:32.317
what kind of position
it will put you in?

00:03:32.625 --> 00:03:34.459
When you are condemned by everyone,

00:03:34.460 --> 00:03:35.778
will you truly have no regrets?

00:03:35.779 --> 00:03:37.259
I will never regret it.

00:03:40.580 --> 00:03:42.780
Then have you
ever hidden anything from me?

00:04:00.175 --> 00:04:01.655
How ridiculous.

00:04:03.499 --> 00:04:05.658
I cannot believe I kept falling for your

00:04:05.659 --> 00:04:07.659
shameless lies again and again.

00:04:08.339 --> 00:04:10.636
You have only
ever treated me as a blade,

00:04:10.637 --> 00:04:12.638
a tool for your use.

00:04:13.012 --> 00:04:14.133
To you,

00:04:14.175 --> 00:04:16.220
there has never been any sincerity.

00:04:16.940 --> 00:04:18.858
Even now, you have never told me

00:04:18.859 --> 00:04:21.099
that your mother is Haitang Madam.

00:04:36.539 --> 00:04:37.659
Song Zhiyun,

00:04:38.859 --> 00:04:40.580
I know you have never trusted me.

00:04:40.859 --> 00:04:42.619
I also know
why you came to the Gu residence.

00:04:45.179 --> 00:04:46.580
And I know

00:04:48.099 --> 00:04:49.336
this cup of wine is poisoned.

00:04:49.337 --> 00:04:52.211
笙ｪKindred souls
meet the light and become one笙ｪ

00:04:52.212 --> 00:05:00.270
笙ｪSo many chapters,
every wound remembered笙ｪ

00:05:00.425 --> 00:05:04.324
笙ｪBack where we once stood,
the blossoms still remain笙ｪ

00:05:04.325 --> 00:05:06.178
笙ｪThe night runs deep like watching eyes笙ｪ

00:05:06.179 --> 00:05:08.061
Do you believe me now?

00:05:08.062 --> 00:05:09.961
笙ｪWave after wave of sorrow笙ｪ

00:05:09.962 --> 00:05:13.561
笙ｪIn exchange, no one will ever know笙ｪ

00:05:13.562 --> 00:05:15.895
笙ｪI will wait笙ｪ

00:05:17.175 --> 00:05:19.661
笙ｪLonging finds no place to rest笙ｪ

00:05:19.662 --> 00:05:21.811
笙ｪThrough drifting wind and rain笙ｪ

00:05:21.812 --> 00:05:25.299
笙ｪYou are the prayer within my hands笙ｪ

00:05:25.300 --> 00:05:32.924
笙ｪA single second frozen,
tears in focus, my heart already knows笙ｪ

00:05:32.925 --> 00:05:35.386
笙ｪWe made a promise long ago笙ｪ

00:05:35.387 --> 00:05:37.386
笙ｪFor all our days to come笙ｪ

00:05:37.387 --> 00:05:41.049
笙ｪYou are the fate I cannot outrun笙ｪ

00:05:41.050 --> 00:05:46.436
笙ｪHow much must I let go
to trade for one moment?笙ｪ

00:05:46.437 --> 00:05:49.057
笙ｪHolding you close笙ｪ

00:05:49.237 --> 00:05:51.557
笙ｪWould that be enough?笙ｪ

00:05:51.739 --> 00:05:52.859
Song Zhiyun,

00:05:53.979 --> 00:05:55.739
you cannot bear for me to die.

00:05:56.112 --> 00:05:58.033
I have won.

00:06:08.862 --> 00:06:12.661
笙ｪYou gave me a silent dream笙ｪ

00:06:12.662 --> 00:06:16.811
笙ｪTime rushed by,
yet the memories linger long笙ｪ

00:06:16.812 --> 00:06:19.949
笙ｪCarrying the weight of hatred笙ｪ

00:06:19.950 --> 00:06:23.945
笙ｪBurying every trace of love笙ｪ

00:06:24.500 --> 00:06:28.486
笙ｪI found a faint light
in the fading dusk笙ｪ

00:06:28.487 --> 00:06:32.086
笙ｪAnd met your steady gaze笙ｪ

00:06:32.087 --> 00:06:40.907
笙ｪOne knowing glance,
and side by side we walk on笙ｪ

00:06:41.350 --> 00:06:43.836
笙ｪLonging finds no place to rest笙ｪ

00:06:43.837 --> 00:06:45.986
笙ｪThrough drifting wind and rain笙ｪ

00:06:45.987 --> 00:06:49.474
笙ｪYou are the prayer within my hands笙ｪ

00:06:49.475 --> 00:06:57.099
笙ｪA single second frozen,
tears in focus, my heart already knows笙ｪ

00:06:57.100 --> 00:06:59.561
笙ｪWe made a promise long ago笙ｪ

00:06:59.562 --> 00:07:01.732
笙ｪFor all our days to come笙ｪ

00:07:02.099 --> 00:07:03.619
Zhiyun,

00:07:04.179 --> 00:07:06.340
we have not yet bowed
before Heaven and Earth.

00:07:06.620 --> 00:07:08.380
This is not proper.

00:07:11.020 --> 00:07:12.619
I will take responsibility for you.

00:07:13.412 --> 00:07:15.732
笙ｪWould that be enough?笙ｪ

00:07:16.437 --> 00:07:19.086
笙ｪLonging finds no place to rest笙ｪ

00:07:19.087 --> 00:07:21.319
笙ｪThrough drifting wind and rain笙ｪ

00:07:21.350 --> 00:07:24.837
笙ｪYou are the prayer within my hands笙ｪ

00:07:24.838 --> 00:07:32.462
笙ｪA single second frozen,
tears in focus, my heart already knows笙ｪ

00:07:32.463 --> 00:07:34.924
笙ｪWe made a promise long ago笙ｪ

00:07:34.925 --> 00:07:36.924
笙ｪFor all our days to come笙ｪ

00:07:36.925 --> 00:07:40.587
笙ｪYou are the fate I cannot outrun笙ｪ

00:07:40.588 --> 00:07:45.974
笙ｪHow much must I let go
to trade for one moment?笙ｪ

00:07:45.975 --> 00:07:48.595
笙ｪHolding you close笙ｪ

00:07:50.512 --> 00:07:52.832
笙ｪWould that be enough?笙ｪ

00:08:00.620 --> 00:08:01.780
Gu Chengye,

00:08:03.260 --> 00:08:04.940
hand over the Beauty Portrait.

00:08:07.580 --> 00:08:08.700
This is bad.

00:08:12.219 --> 00:08:14.460
Shanguan Yu, it is not what you think.

00:08:15.020 --> 00:08:16.259
Why are you here?

00:08:16.260 --> 00:08:17.460
- I...
- Official.

00:08:18.587 --> 00:08:20.798
Commander Gao has lifted
the seal on Huanyue House.

00:08:24.140 --> 00:08:25.340
What are you looking at?

00:08:28.179 --> 00:08:29.739
Lower your bow.

00:08:44.620 --> 00:08:46.259
You cannot even hold your sword steady.

00:08:46.579 --> 00:08:48.460
Do not say you serve under me.

00:08:49.020 --> 00:08:50.180
The Beauty Portrait.

00:08:50.459 --> 00:08:51.700
Enough talk.

00:08:52.140 --> 00:08:53.178
Shanguan Yu,

00:08:53.179 --> 00:08:54.379
I trust you,

00:08:54.380 --> 00:08:55.619
and I trust him.

00:08:55.620 --> 00:08:57.307
There is no need to draw blades.

00:08:58.380 --> 00:08:59.540
If Zhiyun trusts you,

00:08:59.620 --> 00:09:00.619
then so do I.

00:09:01.220 --> 00:09:02.940
I was about to tell her everything.

00:09:03.020 --> 00:09:04.259
If you trust me,

00:09:04.500 --> 00:09:05.619
then come.

00:09:20.740 --> 00:09:22.300
The animals in this painting

00:09:22.779 --> 00:09:23.859
symbolize the powerful nobles

00:09:23.860 --> 00:09:26.340
of the Shengtang Guild hidden
behind their animal masks.

00:09:27.740 --> 00:09:29.060
What is depicted here

00:09:29.260 --> 00:09:30.536
(Haitang Madam)
are their crimes.

00:09:30.537 --> 00:09:32.745
(Haitang Madam)

00:09:34.020 --> 00:09:35.420
This is

00:09:35.500 --> 00:09:36.979
Haitang Madam?

00:09:39.020 --> 00:09:39.979
Yes.

00:09:40.699 --> 00:09:43.379
Mother once founded
the Haitang Guild in the capital.

00:09:43.860 --> 00:09:46.700
Its purpose was to teach women
to read and learn skills.

00:09:47.140 --> 00:09:48.660
Because of that, the court

00:09:48.779 --> 00:09:50.739
bestowed upon her
the title of Haitang Madam.

00:09:52.020 --> 00:09:53.178
But later,

00:09:53.179 --> 00:09:54.779
she died under false accusation.

00:09:55.459 --> 00:09:56.859
I do not know why,

00:09:56.860 --> 00:09:59.019
but the Haitang Guild
became the Shengtang Guild.

00:09:59.459 --> 00:10:00.700
Look at this Beauty Portrait.

00:10:00.939 --> 00:10:02.099
These animals

00:10:02.100 --> 00:10:03.619
are all bowing to my mother.

00:10:04.220 --> 00:10:06.899
It makes her appear
to be the one behind it all.

00:10:09.137 --> 00:10:10.257
Zhiyun,

00:10:11.179 --> 00:10:13.580
before the truth comes to light,

00:10:13.620 --> 00:10:15.099
I truly had no way

00:10:15.179 --> 00:10:16.979
to tell you everything.

00:10:19.860 --> 00:10:21.099
Zhiyun,

00:10:21.962 --> 00:10:24.779
the shades of color
in this painting vary.

00:10:26.020 --> 00:10:27.859
It does not look like
it was made at one time.

00:10:28.500 --> 00:10:29.540
You are right.

00:10:30.050 --> 00:10:33.314
The portraits of Haitang Madam
teaching the performers

00:10:34.020 --> 00:10:36.779
are lighter in color than
the later indecent scenes of the animals.

00:10:36.819 --> 00:10:37.778
That means

00:10:37.779 --> 00:10:40.099
those vile images were added

00:10:40.539 --> 00:10:43.540
after Haitang Madam passed away,

00:10:43.819 --> 00:10:46.940
transforming the Haitang Guild
into the Shengtang Guild.

00:10:47.437 --> 00:10:49.580
I had long suspected

00:10:49.887 --> 00:10:51.979
that although Mother
was said to have hanged herself,

00:10:52.419 --> 00:10:53.820
there were faint traces of blood

00:10:53.900 --> 00:10:55.807
on the white silk.

00:10:57.819 --> 00:10:58.899
Could it be

00:10:58.900 --> 00:11:00.458
that someone used scandal

00:11:00.459 --> 00:11:02.058
to drive the Duchess to her death,

00:11:02.059 --> 00:11:03.818
seized the Haitang Guild,

00:11:03.819 --> 00:11:06.099
and turned it into
this den of corruption?

00:11:07.212 --> 00:11:08.331
Zhiyun,

00:11:09.340 --> 00:11:10.739
thank you for thinking that way.

00:11:11.712 --> 00:11:12.924
However,

00:11:12.925 --> 00:11:16.099
to clear my mother's name and
uncover the truth of the Shengtang Guild,

00:11:16.100 --> 00:11:18.340
the evidence we have

00:11:18.779 --> 00:11:19.899
is still not enough.

00:11:28.512 --> 00:11:29.899
There is a hidden page here.

00:11:42.179 --> 00:11:43.979
Lady Ruyi.

00:11:44.250 --> 00:11:46.859
The Beauty Portrait was Lady Ruyi...

00:11:48.659 --> 00:11:50.700
She is the one
behind the Shengtang Guild.

00:11:52.020 --> 00:11:54.379
The Guild has invited the two of us.

00:11:54.380 --> 00:11:56.979
This may be
our best chance to expose her.

00:11:58.059 --> 00:11:59.180
However,

00:12:00.659 --> 00:12:02.357
it will surely be a trap.

00:12:03.425 --> 00:12:04.706
It seems this time,

00:12:05.100 --> 00:12:06.486
whether we wish to go or not,

00:12:06.487 --> 00:12:08.087
we must go.

00:12:08.525 --> 00:12:10.206
The arrow is already drawn.

00:12:10.380 --> 00:12:12.099
It must strike its mark.

00:12:14.020 --> 00:12:15.139
Shanguan Yu,

00:12:15.275 --> 00:12:17.007
we need your help.

00:12:19.459 --> 00:12:20.940
If Zhiyun trusts you,

00:12:21.620 --> 00:12:23.180
then I will trust you once.

00:12:23.860 --> 00:12:25.460
But if you betray her,

00:12:25.637 --> 00:12:27.379
I will not spare you.

00:12:36.579 --> 00:12:39.395
I have heard people
in the Shengtang Guild mention Lady Ruyi.

00:12:39.740 --> 00:12:41.186
Within the Shengtang Guild,

00:12:41.187 --> 00:12:43.474
she is the most mysterious figure.

00:12:43.475 --> 00:12:44.836
So far,

00:12:44.939 --> 00:12:46.739
the only one who knows her true identity

00:12:46.750 --> 00:12:48.669
is her most trusted confidant.

00:12:50.487 --> 00:12:51.608
Gao Deng.

00:12:55.740 --> 00:12:57.499
The Duchess

00:12:58.020 --> 00:12:59.899
is implicated in this matter.

00:13:00.459 --> 00:13:03.300
It seems he is
the true mastermind behind the Guild.

00:13:04.225 --> 00:13:06.657
No wonder the invitation yesterday

00:13:07.350 --> 00:13:09.591
required me to bring you along.

00:13:10.020 --> 00:13:11.019
It appears

00:13:11.020 --> 00:13:13.420
this banquet is an opportunity.

00:13:15.059 --> 00:13:16.778
By inviting the two of us,

00:13:16.779 --> 00:13:18.540
he intends
to kill two birds with one stone.

00:13:19.819 --> 00:13:21.739
You are the Commander
of the Imperial Guard.

00:13:22.059 --> 00:13:23.540
They must be wary of you

00:13:23.980 --> 00:13:25.739
and will try to win you over.

00:13:25.980 --> 00:13:26.739
As for me,

00:13:26.740 --> 00:13:28.058
I am the only witness.

00:13:28.059 --> 00:13:29.178
They

00:13:29.179 --> 00:13:31.739
will surely try
every means to eliminate me.

00:13:32.579 --> 00:13:33.979
In that case,

00:13:34.659 --> 00:13:35.658
we might as well

00:13:35.659 --> 00:13:37.259
go along with their scheme,

00:13:37.260 --> 00:13:38.779
play it to our advantage,

00:13:38.939 --> 00:13:40.219
step into the trap,

00:13:40.220 --> 00:13:41.619
and draw Lady Ruyi out.